name: Nite Ize Figure 9 Carabiner With Rope
description: Easily achieve and maintain rope tension to secure loads or tighten tent flies with this carabiner rope tightener. Simple tension system for taut and slack-free ropes without fussing with knots and adjustments.Made from cast aluminum with stainless steel spring gate.Fits rope sizes from 2mm to 5mm.Includes 3.1m (5mm) rope.Not to be used for climbing.Sold in pack of 2.
